{
  "info": {
    "name": "Knowledge Platform - Stage 10 全链路集成测试",
    "description": "# 知识库与内容发布平台 — 全链路集成测试\n\n## 覆盖范围 (42 条用例)\n| 模块 | 用例数 | 包含场景 |\n|------|--------|---------|\n| 0-环境检查 | 3 | Nginx可达、Nacos注册、中间件健康 |\n| 1-用户服务 | 6 | 注册/登录/注销/异常/鉴权 |\n| 2-文章服务 | 9 | CRUD/发布/权限/消息发送 |\n| 3-互动服务 | 5 | 评论/点赞/防重/热度联动 |\n| 4-热搜榜单 | 6 | 公开访问/排序/缓存/热度累加 |\n| 5-网关限流 | 3 | 429触发/恢复/公开路径 |\n| 6-异步广播 | 4 | 标签提取/合规检测/违规拦截 |\n| 7-AI续写 | 4 | SSE流式/Demo/断连/校验 |\n| 8-数据一致性 | 4 | Redis↔MySQL/RabbitMQ可靠性 |\n| 9-全流程E2E | 1 | 注册→创作→互动→热搜 一键跑通 |\n\n## 环境变量\n| 变量 | 默认值 | 说明 |\n|------|--------|------|\n| `baseUrl` | `http://localhost` | Nginx入口(80端口) |\n| `token` | (自动) | 用户A Token |\n| `tokenB` | (自动) | 用户B Token |\n| `adminToken` | (自动) | 管理员Token |\n| `articleId` | (自动) | 测试文章ID |\n\n## 执行方式\n1. 导入 Collection → 创建 Environment (baseUrl=http://localhost)\n2. **按文件夹顺序执行** (0→1→2→...→9)\n3. 或使用 Runner: Run Collection → 勾选 \"Keep variable values\" → 全量执行",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "kb-platform-stage10"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "0-环境检查 (Health Check)",
      "description": "验证所有基础设施和服务可达",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "H01: Nginx 代理可达",
          "event": [{"listen": "test", "script": {"exec": ["pm.test('Nginx可达 200', function() { pm.response.to.have.status(200); });", "var json = pm.response.json();", "pm.test('返回 Result<T> 格式', function() { pm.expect(json.code).to.eql(200); });", "console.log('✅ Nginx → Gateway → article-service 全链路通');"], "type": "text/javascript"}}],
          "request": {"method": "GET", "url": {"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/trending", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "trending"]}, "description": "验证 Nginx → Gateway → article-service 全链路"}
        },
        {
          "name": "H02: Gzip 压缩验证",
          "event": [{"listen": "test", "script": {"exec": ["var ce = pm.response.headers.get('Content-Encoding');", "pm.test('Gzip 压缩启用', function() { pm.expect(ce).to.include('gzip'); });", "console.log('Content-Encoding: ' + ce);"], "type": "text/javascript"}}],
          "request": {"method": "GET", "header": [{"key": "Accept-Encoding", "value": "gzip"}], "url": {"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/articles?page=1&size=5", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "articles"], "query": [{"key": "page", "value": "1"}, {"key": "size", "value": "5"}]}, "description": "验证 Nginx Gzip 压缩"}
        },
        {
          "name": "H03: Nacos 服务注册",
          "event": [{"listen": "test", "script": {"exec": ["pm.test('Nacos 可达', function() { pm.response.to.have.status(200); });", "var data = pm.response.text();", "console.log('已注册服务:');", "try { JSON.parse(data).doms.forEach(function(s) { console.log('  - ' + s); }); } catch(e) {}"], "type": "text/javascript"}}],
          "request": {"method": "GET", "url": {"raw": "http://localhost:8848/nacos/v1/ns/service/list?namespaceId=kb-platform", "host": ["localhost"], "path": ["nacos", "v1", "ns", "service", "list"], "query": [{"key": "namespaceId", "value": "kb-platform"}]}, "description": "验证 Nacos 服务注册中心在线"}
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "1-用户服务 (6 cases)",
      "description": "注册、登录、注销、鉴权",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "U01: 注册用户A",
          "event": [{"listen": "test", "script": {"exec": ["var json = pm.response.json();", "if (pm.response.code === 200) { pm.environment.set('usernameA', 'itest_a'); console.log('用户A注册成功'); }", "pm.test('注册成功或已存在', function() { pm.expect([200,400]).to.include(pm.response.code); });"], "type": "text/javascript"}}],
          "request": {"method": "POST", "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}], "body": {"mode": "raw", "raw": "{\"username\":\"itest_a\",\"password\":\"itest123\"}"}, "url": {"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/user/register", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "user", "register"]}}
        },
        {
          "name": "U02: 注册用户B",
          "event": [{"listen": "test", "script": {"exec": ["var json = pm.response.json();", "if (pm.response.code === 200) { pm.environment.set('usernameB', 'itest_b'); console.log('用户B注册成功'); }", "pm.test('注册成功或已存在', function() { pm.expect([200,400]).to.include(pm.response.code); });"], "type": "text/javascript"}}],
          "request": {"method": "POST", "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}], "body": {"mode": "raw", "raw": "{\"username\":\"itest_b\",\"password\":\"itest123\"}"}, "url": {"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/user/register", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "user", "register"]}}
        },
        {
          "name": "U03: 重复注册(异常)",
          "event": [{"listen": "test", "script": {"exec": ["pm.test('返回 400', function() { pm.response.to.have.status(400); });", "pm.test('提示已存在', function() { pm.expect(pm.response.json().message).to.include('已存在'); });"], "type": "text/javascript"}}],
          "request": {"method": "POST", "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}], "body": {"mode": "raw", "raw": "{\"username\":\"itest_a\",\"password\":\"itest123\"}"}, "url": {"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/user/register", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "user", "register"]}}
        },
        {
          "name": "U04: 用户A登录",
          "event": [{"listen": "test", "script": {"exec": ["var json = pm.response.json();", "if (pm.response.code === 200) {", "  pm.environment.set('token', json.data.token);", "  pm.environment.set('userId', json.data.userId);", "  console.log('Token已保存: userId=' + json.data.userId);", "}", "pm.test('登录成功', function() { pm.expect(json.data).to.have.property('token'); pm.expect(json.data).to.have.property('tokenType','Bearer'); });"], "type": "text/javascript"}}],
          "request": {"method": "POST", "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}], "body": {"mode": "raw", "raw": "{\"username\":\"itest_a\",\"password\":\"itest123\"}"}, "url": {"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/user/login", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "user", "login"]}}
        },
        {
          "name": "U05: 用户B登录",
          "event": [{"listen": "test", "script": {"exec": ["var json = pm.response.json();", "if (pm.response.code === 200) {", "  pm.environment.set('tokenB', json.data.token);", "  pm.environment.set('userIdB', json.data.userId);", "}", "pm.test('登录成功', function() { pm.expect(json.data).to.have.property('token'); });"], "type": "text/javascript"}}],
          "request": {"method": "POST", "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}], "body": {"mode": "raw", "raw": "{\"username\":\"itest_b\",\"password\":\"itest123\"}"}, "url": {"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/user/login", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "user", "login"]}}
        },
        {
          "name": "U06: 错误密码(异常)",
          "event": [{"listen": "test", "script": {"exec": ["pm.test('返回 401', function() { pm.response.to.have.status(401); });", "pm.test('错误提示', function() { pm.expect(pm.response.json().message).to.include('错误'); });"], "type": "text/javascript"}}],
          "request": {"method": "POST", "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}], "body": {"mode": "raw", "raw": "{\"username\":\"itest_a\",\"password\":\"wrongpass\"}"}, "url": {"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/user/login", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "user", "login"]}}
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "2-文章服务 (9 cases)",
      "description": "CRUD、发布、权限、消息发送",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "A01: 创建草稿",
          "event": [{"listen": "test", "script": {"exec": ["var json = pm.response.json();", "if (pm.response.code === 200) { pm.environment.set('articleId', json.data.id); console.log('文章ID: ' + json.data.id); }", "pm.test('创建成功 status=DRAFT', function() { pm.expect(json.data.status).to.eql('DRAFT'); });"], "type": "text/javascript"}}],
          "request": {"method": "POST", "header": [{"key": "Content-Type","value": "application/json"},{"key": "Authorization","value": "Bearer {{token}}"}], "body": {"mode": "raw", "raw": "{\"title\":\"集成测试文章 - Spring Boot与Docker实践\",\"content\":\"本文详细介绍了Spring Boot微服务与Docker容器化的最佳实践，包括服务注册发现(Nacos)、API网关(Gateway)、缓存策略(Redis+Caffeine)、消息队列(RabbitMQ)等核心技术栈。\"}"}, "url": {"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/articles", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "articles"]}}
        },
        {
          "name": "A02: 发布文章",
          "event": [{"listen": "test", "script": {"exec": ["pm.test('发布成功', function() { pm.expect(pm.response.json().data.status).to.eql('PUBLISHED'); });", "console.log('文章已发布 → RabbitMQ消息已发送');"], "type": "text/javascript"}}],
          "request": {"method": "PUT", "header": [{"key": "Authorization","value": "Bearer {{token}}"}], "url": {"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/articles/{{articleId}}/publish", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "articles", "{{articleId}}", "publish"]}}
        },
        {
          "name": "A03: 修改文章",
          "event": [{"listen": "test", "script": {"exec": ["pm.test('修改成功', function() { pm.response.to.have.status(200); });"], "type": "text/javascript"}}],
          "request": {"method": "PUT", "header": [{"key": "Content-Type","value": "application/json"},{"key": "Authorization","value": "Bearer {{token}}"}], "body": {"mode": "raw", "raw": "{\"title\":\"(已修改) Spring Boot与Docker实践 v2\"}"}, "url": {"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/articles/{{articleId}}", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "articles", "{{articleId}}"]}}
        },
        {
          "name": "A04: 越权修改(异常)",
          "event": [{"listen": "test", "script": {"exec": ["pm.test('越权返回403', function() { pm.response.to.have.status(403); });", "pm.test('无权操作', function() { pm.expect(pm.response.json().message).to.include('无权'); });"], "type": "text/javascript"}}],
          "request": {"method": "PUT", "header": [{"key": "Content-Type","value": "application/json"},{"key": "Authorization","value": "Bearer {{tokenB}}"}], "body": {"mode": "raw", "raw": "{\"title\":\"用户B尝试修改\"}"}, "url": {"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/articles/{{articleId}}", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "articles", "{{articleId}}"]}, "description": "用户B 不是作者，无权修改"}
        },
        {
          "name": "A05: 文章列表",
          "event": [{"listen": "test", "script": {"exec": ["pm.test('列表返回数组', function() { pm.expect(pm.response.json().data).to.be.an('array'); });", "var len = pm.response.json().data.length;", "console.log('文章列表: ' + len + ' 条');"], "type": "text/javascript"}}],
          "request": {"method": "GET", "url": {"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/articles?page=1&size=10", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "articles"], "query": [{"key": "page","value": "1"},{"key": "size","value": "10"}]}}
        },
        {
          "name": "A06: 文章详情(触发阅读热度)",
          "event": [{"listen": "test", "script": {"exec": ["pm.test('详情返回', function() { pm.expect(pm.response.json().data).to.have.property('content'); });", "console.log('阅读热度+1 (如5分钟内未重复)');"], "type": "text/javascript"}}],
          "request": {"method": "GET", "header": [{"key": "Authorization","value": "Bearer {{tokenB}}"}], "url": {"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/articles/{{articleId}}", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "articles", "{{articleId}}"]}}
        },
        {
          "name": "A07: 无认证访问(异常)",
          "event": [{"listen": "test", "script": {"exec": ["pm.test('无认证返回401', function() { pm.response.to.have.status(401); });"], "type": "text/javascript"}}],
          "request": {"method": "POST", "header": [{"key": "Content-Type","value": "application/json"}], "body": {"mode": "raw", "raw": "{\"title\":\"test\"}"}, "url": {"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/articles", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "articles"]}, "description": "不带 Token 创建文章"}
        },
        {
          "name": "A08: 逻辑删除",
          "event": [{"listen": "test", "script": {"exec": ["pm.test('删除成功', function() { pm.response.to.have.status(200); });", "console.log('文章已逻辑删除');"], "type": "text/javascript"}}],
          "request": {"method": "DELETE", "header": [{"key": "Authorization","value": "Bearer {{token}}"}], "url": {"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/articles/{{articleId}}", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "articles", "{{articleId}}"]}}
        },
        {
          "name": "A09: 重新创建并发布(准备工作)",
          "event": [{"listen": "test", "script": {"exec": ["var json = pm.response.json();", "if (pm.response.code === 200) { pm.environment.set('articleId', json.data.id); }", "pm.test('新文章已创建并发布', function() { pm.expect(json.data.status).to.eql('PUBLISHED'); });", "console.log('新文章ID: ' + json.data.id + ' → 用于后续互动测试');"], "type": "text/javascript"}}],
          "request": {"method": "POST", "header": [{"key": "Content-Type","value": "application/json"},{"key": "Authorization","value": "Bearer {{token}}"}], "body": {"mode": "raw", "raw": "{\"title\":\"集成测试文章 v2\",\"content\":\"这是一篇用于集成测试的文章，涵盖微服务架构、Docker部署、Redis缓存、RabbitMQ消息队列等内容。\",\"status\":\"PUBLISHED\"}"}, "url": {"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/articles", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "articles"]}, "description": "重新创建一篇已发布状态的文章供后续测试"}
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "3-互动服务 (5 cases)",
      "description": "评论、点赞、防重、热度联动",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "I01: 用户B评论",
          "event": [{"listen": "test", "script": {"exec": ["pm.test('评论成功', function() { pm.response.to.have.status(200); });", "console.log('评论已提交（异步入库）');"], "type": "text/javascript"}}],
          "request": {"method": "POST", "header": [{"key": "Content-Type","value": "application/json"},{"key": "Authorization","value": "Bearer {{tokenB}}"}], "body": {"mode": "raw", "raw": "{\"articleId\":{{articleId}},\"content\":\"非常棒的分享！Spring Boot+Docker的实践总结得很到位。\"}"}, "url": {"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/comments", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "comments"]}}
        },
        {
          "name": "I02: 用户B点赞",
          "event": [{"listen": "test", "script": {"exec": ["pm.test('点赞成功', function() { pm.response.to.have.status(200); });", "console.log('点赞成功 heat +3');"], "type": "text/javascript"}}],
          "request": {"method": "POST", "header": [{"key": "Authorization","value": "Bearer {{tokenB}}"}], "url": {"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/articles/{{articleId}}/like", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "articles", "{{articleId}}", "like"]}}
        },
        {
          "name": "I03: 重复点赞(异常)",
          "event": [{"listen": "test", "script": {"exec": ["pm.test('重复点赞 400', function() { pm.response.to.have.status(400); });", "pm.test('提示已点赞', function() { pm.expect(pm.response.json().message).to.include('已点赞'); });"], "type": "text/javascript"}}],
          "request": {"method": "POST", "header": [{"key": "Authorization","value": "Bearer {{tokenB}}"}], "url": {"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/articles/{{articleId}}/like", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "articles", "{{articleId}}", "like"]}}
        },
        {
          "name": "I04: 再次评论(无防重)",
          "event": [{"listen": "test", "script": {"exec": ["pm.test('第2次评论成功', function() { pm.response.to.have.status(200); });", "console.log('评论无防重，heat再+1');"], "type": "text/javascript"}}],
          "request": {"method": "POST", "header": [{"key": "Content-Type","value": "application/json"},{"key": "Authorization","value": "Bearer {{tokenB}}"}], "body": {"mode": "raw", "raw": "{\"articleId\":{{articleId}},\"content\":\"再来一条评论～\"}"}, "url": {"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/comments", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "comments"]}}
        },
        {
          "name": "I05: 验证Redis热度",
          "event": [{"listen": "test", "script": {"exec": ["console.log('');", "console.log('===== 请在终端执行以下命令验证 =====');", "var aid = pm.environment.get('articleId');", "console.log('docker exec kb-redis redis-cli ZSCORE hot_articles ' + aid);", "console.log('预期: > 5 (阅读1+点赞3+2条评论*1)');"], "type": "text/javascript"}}],
          "request": {"method": "GET", "url": {"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/trending", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "trending"]}, "description": "在 Postman Console 中查看 Redis 验证命令"}
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "4-热搜榜单 (6 cases)",
      "description": "公开访问、排序、缓存、热度累加",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "T01: 公开访问(无Token)",
          "event": [{"listen": "test", "script": {"exec": ["pm.test('公开访问200', function() { pm.response.to.have.status(200); });", "pm.test('返回数组', function() { pm.expect(pm.response.json().data).to.be.an('array'); });"], "type": "text/javascript"}}],
          "request": {"method": "GET", "url": {"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/trending", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "trending"]}}
        },
        {
          "name": "T02: 榜单降序验证",
          "event": [{"listen": "test", "script": {"exec": ["var data = pm.response.json().data;", "if (data.length >= 2) {", "  var sorted = true;", "  for (var i = 1; i < data.length; i++) { if (data[i].heatScore > data[i-1].heatScore) sorted = false; }", "  pm.test('按热度降序', function() { pm.expect(sorted).to.be.true; });", "}", "data.forEach(function(item,i) { console.log((i+1)+'. '+item.title+' heat='+item.heatScore); });"], "type": "text/javascript"}}],
          "request": {"method": "GET", "url": {"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/trending", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "trending"]}}
        },
        {
          "name": "T03: Nginx 缓存验证",
          "event": [{"listen": "test", "script": {"exec": ["var cs = pm.response.headers.get('X-Cache-Status');", "console.log('X-Cache-Status: ' + (cs || '未设置'));", "if (cs) { pm.test('Nginx 缓存头存在', function() { pm.expect(cs).to.be.oneOf(['HIT','MISS','EXPIRED','UPDATING']); }); } else { console.log('(缓存头不存在 - 可能直连Gateway)'); }"], "type": "text/javascript"}}],
          "request": {"method": "GET", "url": {"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/trending", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "trending"]}, "description": "验证 Nginx 代理缓存是否生效"}
        },
        {
          "name": "T04: 连续请求(缓存命中)",
          "event": [{"listen": "test", "script": {"exec": ["var t = pm.response.responseTime;", "var prev = pm.environment.get('prevTrendingTime');", "console.log('响应时间: ' + t + 'ms (上次: ' + (prev||'N/A') + 'ms)');", "pm.environment.set('prevTrendingTime', t);", "if (prev && parseInt(t) < 5 && parseInt(prev) < 5) { console.log('✅ 连续请求均 <5ms — 缓存命中'); }"], "type": "text/javascript"}}],
          "request": {"method": "GET", "url": {"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/trending", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "trending"]}, "description": "1秒内重复执行此请求 — 观察缓存命中效果"}
        },
        {
          "name": "T05: 空榜单处理",
          "event": [{"listen": "test", "script": {"exec": ["pm.test('空榜单仍返回200', function() { pm.response.to.have.status(200); });", "pm.test('data为[]而非null', function() { var d = pm.response.json().data; pm.expect(d).to.be.an('array'); });"], "type": "text/javascript"}}],
          "request": {"method": "GET", "url": {"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/trending", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "trending"]}, "description": "验证 ZSET 为空时不报错"}
        },
        {
          "name": "T06: TopArticleVO 字段完整性",
          "event": [{"listen": "test", "script": {"exec": ["var items = pm.response.json().data;", "if (items.length > 0) {", "  var first = items[0];", "  pm.test('含id', function() { pm.expect(first).to.have.property('id'); });", "  pm.test('含title', function() { pm.expect(first).to.have.property('title'); });", "  pm.test('含authorId', function() { pm.expect(first).to.have.property('authorId'); });", "  pm.test('含likeCount', function() { pm.expect(first).to.have.property('likeCount'); });", "  pm.test('含heatScore', function() { pm.expect(first.heatScore).to.be.a('number'); });", "}"], "type": "text/javascript"}}],
          "request": {"method": "GET", "url": {"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/trending", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "trending"]}}
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "5-网关限流 (3 cases)",
